<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>We walked into the station right when you came up to make the call after a fatal accident. </p> <p>Even though you were on the phone with EMS you took a moment to warn me not to take my daughter down to track level. </p> <p>Thank you. That really made a world of difference for us. </p> <p>I hope you and your daughter are all right.</p> <p>.</p> <p>I know it&#39;s a long shot posting on here, but if you know this woman, can you please pass on my thanks?</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/YESmynameisYes"> /u/YESmynameisYes </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/toronto/comments/bwepu7/eglinton_station_yesterday_to_the_woman_who_was/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/toronto/comments/bwepu7/eglinton_station_yesterday_to_the_woman_who_was/">[comments]</a></span>